Project Basic Guidelines 

- We are using `bun`, not `npm`
- Vue 3 web framework
- All code is in TypeScript, even inside .vue files `<script>`
- All Vue components are written in `<script setup lang="ts">` format
- Using Bootstrap 5 as UI library via the `bootstrap-vue-next` plugin
- Using icons from Lucide via `lucide-vue-next` plugin
